PrecisRe-appointment of PAULAH JEAN DAUNS, of North Vancouver, British Columbia, and FRED HITCHCOCK, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective August 10, 2001.
